            "last_activity_date": 1295296043,
            "creation_date": 1295296043,
            "body": "<p>I don't know much about C# but the <code>Main()<\/code> method is static, while <code>LaunchMinecraft()\n<\/code> isn't, that's the cause of this error. <\/p>\n",
